{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"6":"Chapters Regarding Funerals"},"section_detail":{"6":{"hadithnumber_first":1433,"hadithnumber_last":1637,"arabicnumber_first":1433,"arabicnumber_last":1637}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1479,"arabicnumber":1479,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Musa : Le Prophète (ﷺ) a vu un cortège funèbre où les gens se dépêchaient. Il a dit : “Vous devez avancer avec calme.”","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Munkar"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Munkar"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":6,"hadith":47}}]}